data.description: Recently remodeled home conveniently located off of Highway 58. Living rooms and bedrooms feature LVP. Kitchen has tile flooring, stainless steel appliances, white shaker cabinets and beautiful butcher block countertops. 2 bedrooms upstairs with plenty of closet space. One full bathroom in hallway with jetted tub and one full bathroom in Primary bedroom with walk in shower. One bedroom downstairs and laundry room. Large, fully fenced, backyard is the perfect spot to relax around the fire pit this winter! Come see all this home has to offer today!
